{"start": "20251211_122327", "end": "20251211_122327", "time": 0.0028901100158691406, "tool_name": "query_db", "result": {"success": true, "preview": "[{\"Id\": \"001Wt00000PFj50IAD\", \"Name\": \"FusionTech Systems\", \"Description\": \"FusionTech Systems stands out in technology manufacturing by integrating AI and cloud-based solutions. With products like AI Cirku-Tech and CloudLink Designer, they commit to providing innovative manufacturing processes. Their dedication to tech-driven manufacturing ensures high-quality, reliable outputs.\"}, {\"Id\": \"#001Wt00000PFlupIAD\", \"Name\": \"NeuralWave Technologies\", \"Description\": \"NeuralWave Technologies leads advancements in AI-driven solutions for various applications. Using products like AI Cirku-Tech and Workflow Genius, they optimize design processes and enhance power management in AI systems. Focused on innovation, they continue to push the boundaries of artificial intelligence capabilities.\"}, {\"Id\": \"001Wt00000PFsjOIAT\", \"Name\": \"QuantumLeap Computing\", \"Description\": \"QuantumLeap Computing pushes the boundaries of quantum technology with their advanced solutions. With QuantumPCB Modeler and AI Cirku-Tech, they offer cutting-edge computational capabilities. Their relentless pursuit of innovation positions them at the forefront of the quantum computing industry.\"}, {\"Id\": \"001Wt00000PGQzcIAH\", \"Name\": \"UrbanEDGE Innovation\", \"Description\": \"UrbanEDGE Innovation drives the growth of smart cities through advanced circuit and security technologies. Utilizing AI Cirku-Tech and CircuitMaster Analyzer, they create efficient and secure urban solutions. Their vision for the future of cities includes smarter infrastructures and seamless technology integration.\"}, {\"Id\": \"001Wt00000PGYx4IAH\", \"Name\": \"UrbanSmart Inc.\", \"Description\": \"UrbanSmart Inc. leads the innovation of smart infrastructure projects through seamless integration of security and AI technologies. With products like SecureFlow Suite and AI Cirku-Tech, they enhance urban planning and development efficiency, building smarter cities for the future.\"}, {\"Id\": \"001Wt00000PGoAaIAL\", \"Name\": \"TrueNorth Technologies\", \"Description\": \"TrueNorth Technologies offers specialized consulting services to businesses aiming to enhance their technological infrastructure. Utilizing EduTech Lab and AI Cirku-Tech, they deliver tailored solutions that improve clients' operational efficiencies. Their experienced team of consultants ensures seamless integration and superior support.\"}, {\"Id\": \"001Wt00000PGzsMIAT\", \"Name\": \"PrimeEdge Technology   \", \"Description\": \"PrimeEdge Technology excels in providing cutting-edge IT solutions that focus on AI-driven analytics and workflow automation. Leveraging products like AI Cirku-Tech and SecureAnalytics Pro, they empower businesses to optimize processes and secure their data. Their visionary approach positions them as leaders in the IT industry.\"}]"}, "args": {"query": "SELECT Id, Name, Description FROM Account WHERE Name LIKE '%Cirku%' OR Description LIKE '%Cirku%'", "db_name": "core_crm"}, "val_args": {"db_type": "sqlite", "exec_args": {"db_path": "/home/ruiying/DataAgentBench/query_crmarenapro/query_dataset/core_crm.db", "sql": "SELECT Id, Name, Description FROM Account WHERE Name LIKE '%Cirku%' OR Description LIKE '%Cirku%'"}}}
